title: First in Class and Bottom of the Pack: Grading the Teams of the Women’s WorldTour – Part 1
content:
SD Worx was the A+ student in 2023, dominating nearly every race it entered, while Liv Racing TeqFind failed to hit the mark after a below-par year.

Read the full article at First in Class and Bottom of the Pack: Grading the Teams of the Women’s WorldTour – Part 1 on Velo.
